<subSubSection id="C30198A6FFF8FFC0FF02FA0AFD8B73A6" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA4CB2DFFF8FFC0FF02FA0AFF2570C6" blockId="4.[130,777,1430,1743]" box="[132,207,1430,1456]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">NOTES</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BA4CB2DFFF8FFC0FF02FA2AFD8B73A6" blockId="4.[130,777,1430,1743]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF8FFC0FF02FA2AFE8470A7" author="LECOMTE H." box="[132,366,1461,1488]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" pagination="99 - 121" refId="ref13173" refString="LECOMTE H. 1928 a. - Ebenacees nouvelles de l'Indochine. Notulae Systematicae 4 (4): 99 - 121. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 6463259" type="journal article" year="1928">Lecomte (1928a: 112)</bibRefCitation>
cited two gatherings in the protologue: 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FF04FA4AFF1B7087" box="[130,241,1493,1519]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Bon 5215</emphasis>
from “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FEC0FA49FE777087" box="[326,413,1493,1519]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Tonkin</collectingCountry>
, Phudién”, and 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FDDCFA4AFD237087" box="[602,713,1493,1519]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Bon 2758</emphasis>
from “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FF16FA69FF0E7367" box="[144,228,1525,1551]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Tonkin</collectingCountry>
, Lat son”, introducing the latter as a variant of the species with leaves more oval. Subsequently, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF8FFC0FDDDF98AFF5D7338" author="LECOMTE H." pageId="4" pageNumber="117" pagination="915 - 978" refId="ref13275" refString="LECOMTE H. 1930. - Ebenacees, in LECOMTE H. &amp; HUMBERT H. (eds), Flore generale de l'Indo-Chine. Vol. 3. Masson &amp; Co., Paris: 915 - 978. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 27563332" type="book chapter" year="1930">Lecomte (1930: 960)</bibRefCitation>
cited only “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FEB6F9A9FE697327" box="[304,387,1589,1615]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Tonkin</collectingCountry>
: Phù-diên (
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FE7CF9AAFDC97327" box="[506,547,1590,1615]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Bon</emphasis>
)”, omitting the other. 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF8FFC0FF04F9C9FEB27318" author="NGUYEN T. H." box="[130,344,1621,1648]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" pagination="63 - 74" refId="ref13500" refString="NGUYEN T. H. 1996. - Fam. Ebenaceae Gurke, in AVERYANOV L. V., NGUYEN T. B., NGUYEN T. H., PHAN K. L., SEROV V. P. &amp; AKIMOVA G. A. (eds), Vascular Plants Synopsis of Vietnamese Flora. Russian Academy of Sciences, Saint Petersburg, Russia and National Center for Natural Sciences and Technology of Vietnam: 63 - 74." type="book chapter" year="1996">Nguyen (1996: 64)</bibRefCitation>
cited 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FE18F9CAFDE27307" box="[414,520,1621,1647]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Bon 5215</emphasis>
(P) as 
<typeStatus id="54A0758FFFF8FFC0FDD3F9C9FD5E7307" box="[597,692,1621,1647]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">holotype</typeStatus>
but we found four sheets of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FED3F9E9FE5073E7" box="[341,442,1653,1679]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Bon 5215</emphasis>
at P. The specimen P00721446, the only sheet bearing Lecomte’s determination and type annotation, is designated here as the 
<typeStatus id="54A0758FFFF8FFC0FE7EF928FDB773A6" box="[504,605,1716,1742]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
